{"tid":1118230,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"曹查理, 徐少強既咸濕底線","createTime":"2019-04-21T09:12:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T09:33:48.000Z","uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"004e4d24b5c501efc1c7f845ceecb50bfcb89dae","tid":1118230,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:12:20.000Z","msg":"最近安心單野, 令我諗起老牌影星既咸濕底線<br />\n<br />\n徐少強話佢自己鐘意去蒲去夜總會, 但佢永遠都唔會搞女演員, 正所謂『好兔不吃窩邊草。』<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20170408/56539539\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170408%2F56539539&d=CcUT5H46krin9iWjsTG5RAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=c31b2126\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170408%2F56539539&h=0f598b86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20170408/56539539</a><br />\n<br />\n曹查理亦講過佢唔會借住拍三級片去享受艷褔, 要『搵食』會自己出去搵. (意指唔會搞女演員)<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190326/59359988\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190326%2F59359988&d=CcUT5H46krin9iWjsTG5RAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=42c6c8a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190326%2F59359988&h=32240998\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190326/59359988</a><br />\n<br />\n我朋友既朋友都聽過某老牌影星講咸濕底線. &nbsp;老牌影星話點淫都好, 以下兩類人係絕對唔可以淫 (因拍拖戀愛而做愛無問題, 但千萬不能『有性無愛』)<br />\nA: 圈內人, 包括女演員.<br />\nB: 女fans<br />\n<br />\n當然有唔人唔守規舉而比傳媒唱通街, 但亦有唔少著名影星都堅守咸濕底線, 結果依然保持形象健康 (包括果位老牌影星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />). &nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n古天樂拍既咸片《豪情》入面有段金句: 「<strong>每個人每做一件事都應該有一條底線，呢條底線第日會救你一命.</strong>」 呢句絕對係至理名言"},{"pid":"3045d09c3038605b0a39a572b981cfa59dcfc8a2","tid":1118230,"uid":182930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:15:04.000Z","msg":"徐少強條友都食唔少先離婚架啦<br />\n早兩年同個大陸妹一齊<br />\n條女爆曬佢啲野出嚟佢就話要告人<br />\n咪笑大人個口啦佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3cb0caed95d01c1447bcb720dbf4e180d957c94","tid":1118230,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:18:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>徐少強條友都食唔少先離婚架啦<br />\n早兩年同個大陸妹一齊<br />\n條女爆曬佢啲野出嚟佢就話要告人<br />\n咪笑大人個口啦佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n徐少強:「國語有句﹕『好兔不吃窩邊草。』大膽講句，我有咩收工都去夜總會，我鍾意飲酒去蒲，痴線嘅，但我永遠唔會搞女演員。」<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20170408/56539539\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170408%2F56539539&d=CcUT5H46krin9iWjsTG5RAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=c31b2126\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170408%2F56539539&h=0f598b86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20170408/56539539</a>"},{"pid":"31c3cc4162a013ed2b8d84c5d57db698d49fda00","tid":1118230,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:19:23.000Z","msg":"《豪情》古天樂角色既真人原型, 比電影角色更守底線<br />\n<a href=\"https://ent.qq.com/a/20130905/000226_all.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fent.qq.com%2Fa%2F20130905%2F000226_all.htm&d=CcUT5H46krin9iWjsTG5RAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=e4d54299\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ent.qq.com/a/20130905/000226_all.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n狷者鐘健強，在色情雜志的經營中，著意於&ldquo;有所不為&rdquo;。他給員工立下規矩：不能收色情場所的錢寫文章(微博)，工作期間不能嫖妓，否則開除。千禧年後，香港警方抓捕一批淫業大亨，許多色情雜志主事者因涉嫌收受黑錢，也被抓捕，但鐘健強未受影響。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;其實在色情雜志這個行業，本來就是應該這樣的（收黑錢、收宣傳費），只是我不這樣而已。在這個行業裡，我是異類。許多人都說我是冥頑不靈。&rdquo;鐘健強說。攝影師老方告訴他，在內地，收錢寫的文章叫&ldquo;軟文&rdquo;。鐘健強說：&ldquo;我不允許有軟文出現。要那樣的話，寧願免費給色情場所寫文章。&rdquo;他向我們透露，當初工作的那本雜志的風月版被拿掉，就是因為有太多記者編輯收錢寫文章。<br />\n<br />\n人物周刊：在電影《豪情》裡，古天樂飾演的角色和妓女發生了性關系。而古天樂演的就是你。你辦色情雜志的時候，有那樣做過嗎？<br />\n<br />\n鐘健強：沒有！不管你信不信都好。那時候我覺得，做這一行的大部分都不是好人，我不想跟這些人有瓜葛，不想欠他們的東西，我寧願他們欠我的東西。全行業的人都清楚，如果被我知道員工嫖妓不給錢&mdash;&mdash;嫖妓已經不正確了，還敢不給錢？我是馬上炒掉他的。也因為這個原因，炒了很多員工。"},{"pid":"1d1600683ec33c6bd39366700697fa69cd9ae8bf","tid":1118230,"uid":182930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3cb0caed95d01c1447bcb720dbf4e180d957c94","tid":1118230,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:18:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>徐少強條友都食唔少先離婚架啦<br />\n早兩年同個大陸妹一齊<br />\n條女爆曬佢啲野出嚟佢就話要告人<br />\n咪笑大人個口啦佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n徐少強:「國語有句﹕『好兔不吃窩邊草。』大膽講句，我有咩收工都去夜總會，我鍾意飲酒去蒲，痴線嘅，但我永遠唔會搞女演員。」<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20170408/56539539\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170408%2F56539539&d=CcUT5H46krin9iWjsTG5RAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=c31b2126\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170408%2F56539539&h=0f598b86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20170408/56539539</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T09:33:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u3gG7FQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu3gG7FQ.png&h=e1ce7970&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}